import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom/client"
import App from "./App"
import {BrowserRouter} from "react-router-dom"
const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById("root"))
//给整个App加路由
root.render(
    <BrowserRouter>
        <App/>
    </BrowserRouter>
    )
